Perlbrew
========


Installing perl module dependencies using [Perlbrew](https://perlbrew.pl).

```bash
## Select perl version
perlbrew use perl-5.24.0

## Create local::lib environment
perlbrew lib create gff

## Switch to environment
perlbrew use perl-5.24.0@gff

cpanm --installdeps .

## choose your database engine
cpanm --installdeps --with-feature=mysql .
cpanm --installdeps --with-feature=sqlite .
```

You should now have all the dependencies to run `validate_gff3.pl`.
